These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, april
House: farmhouse, art-deco
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
2 different pets are kept: bird, fish
1. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
3. the art-deco house is the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Birthday      | december  | april   |
| House   | art-deco     | farmhouse   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Pet     | bird | fish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, azure
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, documentary
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, pall-mall
House: modern, cottage
1. the pall-mall-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching action movies is the cottage house##1
3. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Color          | coral     | azure |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  |
| Cigar           | pall-mall         | blend     |
| House     | modern   | cottage    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, february
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, techno
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: weightlifting, golf
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the fan of techno##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Birthday    | february     | august |
| Music-Genre         | techno | soul    |
| Sport         | weightlifting         | golf        |
| Transport   | bike         | helicopter    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
