The people have 2 different jobs:  freelancer, accountant
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, cooking
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, crime
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the accountant is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
3. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Cigar      | bolivar     | vegafina |
| Job          | accountant   | freelancer  |
| Hobby         | card-games | cooking     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama  | crime         |

