.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, electrician
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, snowmobile
City: boston, liverpool
House: gothic-revival, wooden
1. the wooden house is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
3. the electrician is the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | electrician | coach    |
| Transport   | skateboard       | snowmobile |
| City           | boston         | liverpool    |
| House         | gothic-revival    | wooden   |

