.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, rowing
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, doctor
City: rome, paris
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, orange
1. the doctor is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
3. the person who likes lavender is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Sport    | baseball | rowing    |
| Job         | doctor        | designer |
| City         | rome          | paris     |
| Color   | lavender        | orange     |

 